decision_conditions:
&lt;p&gt;Prior to the first occupation of the development hereby approved a
minimum of 4 Swift and/or bat nesting bricks shall be provided at or close to
eaves level of the development hereby approved. The bricks/boxes shall be
retained thereafter in perpetuity.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;
REASON: in the interests of biodiversity.&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
